These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | volleyball | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, banana, lime
1. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | cherry | lime | banana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | puzzles | gardening | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, punk, ambient
1. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | blues | ambient | punk |

 #################################

 
